program enlists sailors for general detail the deck and 
engineering assignments that are often dirty laborintensive and 
hard to fill 
these are tough jobs boorda said 
he envisions bringing 2000 such sailors into the service this 
year 14000 over the next year now 580000 men and women serve 
in the navy 
