the woman known as the central park jogger 
climbed unsteadily onto the witness stand monday and described the 
lasting effects of a beating she barely survived and does not 
remember 
speaking in a firm voice the woman testified she has trouble 
walking and seeing cannot smell and cannot remember why 
she said she remembers breaking a dinner date with a friend on 
