view of the german democratic republic 
4 the unified germany concludes with the soviet union a 
bilateral treaty to carry out the withdrawal of soviet troops from 
the german democratic republic that should be concluded within 
three to four years at the same time we should conclude a 
transitional treaty with the soviet union that would cover the 
