democratic republic within this time period from three to four 
years 
5 as long as the soviet troops remain stationed on the former 
territory the german democratic republic the nato structures will 
not be extended to this part of germany the immediate application 
of article 5 and 6 of the nato treaty remains from the beginning 
undisturbed unintegrated units of the bundeswehr the west german 
army that means units of the territorial defense can be 
stationed immediately after unification on the territory of the 
german democratic republic and berlin for the period of the 
