clergyman and wife of a retired foreign service officer she and 
her husband come in every sunday from suburban mclean va but her 
involvement with the cathedral doesnt end there 
on monday afternoons from 1230 to 3 mrs goodchild a former 
schoolteacher goes to a school in a povertystricken area of 
washington and tutors two hispanic fifthgraders 
