the us government or the national episcopal church it is the 
official seat of the presiding bishop of the church but his office 
is in new york 
over the years many washington churches have come to call 
themselves national there are national presbyterian church 
national city christian church national baptist memorial church 
and the national shrine of the immaculate conception among others 
