how they are supplied the executive said quality cost and 
delivery speed determine whether a part or component will be made 
at a ford plant the union wants that work done at plants rather 
than having the work sent to a company where labor is cheaper 
if negotiations proceed as they have in the past the union will 
bargain with each of the big three through july and august 
sometime around labor day the uaw will pick a target company 
