the workers current contract was negotiated following a 98day 
work stoppage that began in 1985 after wheelingpittsburgh filed 
for protection from creditors under chapter 11 of federal 
bankruptcy laws it will expire 10 days after a plan of 
reorganization is approved 
the unions membership unhappy with terms of the reorganization 
plan recently completed polling that gave negotiators the 
